gomodel:SYNGO_3043  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: In Fig 1D super-resolution structured illumination (SIM) microscopy is used to localize C1ql3 between presynaptic Bassoon and postsynaptic PSD-95 immunoreactivities.. Experimental description: Endogenous C1ql2, C1ql3, and GluK2/3 immunoreactivities in WT hippocampus. Arrows indicate CA3 stratum lucidum. Insets show immunoreactivity in mice\nlacking a corresponding gene to confirm antibody specificity. (Legend Fig. 1A, p. 754)" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9681-3318" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9880-1214" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0269-0311" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9377-7414" ;
